#: internal/secrets/service_linux.go:48
msgid ""
"Your secret service provider was found, but refused to interact with "
"Tonearm.\n"
"\n"
"This could because you cancelled a prompt or, if you are using a Flatpak, "
"the provider not implementing the XDG Secret Portal service.\n"
"\n"
"Tonearm will not be able to store any authentication-related data and you "
"will not be able to sign in."
msgstr ""
"Salajase teenuse teenusepakkuja on olemas, kuid ta keeldub Tonearmiga "
"suhtlemast.\n"
"\n"
"See võis juhtuda, kui sulgesid vastava päringu. Kui kasutad Flatpakki, siis "
"võib põhjuseks olla ka see, et teenusepakkujal on „XDG Secret Portal“ teenus "
"implementeerimata.\n"
"\n"
"Tonearm ei suuda salvestada autentimisega seotud andmeid ja sa ei saa sisse "
"logida."

